      "value": "<p>Drawing your weapon is pure reflex when you sense danger.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.0H0bEoQ96KX05ke2]{Improved Initiative} or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.Yw2BRG4gk46kyCL6]{Quick Draw}</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You can draw a one-handed weapon or a weapon that benefits from your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.bMZTC3m95OSPFlTG]{Weapon Focus} feat as part of rolling initiative. You don’t gain the benefit of this feat during a surprise round in which you can’t act. You can’t draw a hidden weapon in this way.</p>"
